Localization.Name: Zenith "Darkwave" Laser Sniper Rifle
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Verified Offworld Laser Technologies
Item Type: Sniper Rifle
Class: Energy (Laser)

Battery Size: 22
Rate of Fire: 60-300 rpm
Effective Range: 80 m

Attachments: Optics (S3), Underbarrel (S2)

The Zenith Laser Sniper Rifle from VOLT offers operational flexibility on the battlefield as it can fire lower-energy shots rapidly, or be allowed time to automatically charge to fire a much more powerful energy blast that also generates significantly more noise and heat.

This Darkwave edition draws attention to the sharp contours and edges of the rifle's design.

Localization.Name: FarSight "Darkwave" (8x Telescopic)
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: VOLT
Type: Telescopic
Attachment Point: Optic
Magnification: 8x
Aim Time: +0%
Size: 3

Designed for long distance precision shooting, the FarSight is carefully crafted to provide unparalleled fidelity of targets. VOLT's TruePicture lens technology provides high levels of light transmission, ensuring easy target acquisition and daylight illumination so you always get your mark.

This Darkwave edition draws attention to the sharp contours and edges of the rifle's design.
